Dear Sirs,
.sk
.us Payment orders in favour of our customers.
.sk
We have been reviewing our incoming payment orders during the months
&SALPARAM01 and note that some payments originating from your bank in
favour of our customers were effected through other danish banks. Please
refer to the encl. lists.
.sk
In order that such payments may reach our customers without delay and
that they may avoid the payment of additional bank charges we ask you
kindly to ensure that such payment orders are sent directly to our bank by
SWIFT MT100. Dependent on the currency involved, please cover us with one
of our correspondent banks according to the enclosed list of our principal
correspondents. In case of DKK, you may cover us with any danish bank.
.sk
We hope for your understanding in this matter, and will take advantage
of the possibilities that the SWIFT Authenticator between our two banks
offer, and send the payment orders directly to
SALLING BANK A/S.
.sk
Please do not hesitate to contact us, if you have som questions.
.sp 15mm
Yours faithfully
